ers','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> Talon of Horus; Drachâ€™nyen.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Abaddon-The-Despoiler'),(925,'Huron Blackheart','CSM',12,'Reviled as the Tyrant of Badab, Huron directs the pitiless reaving of his Red Corsairs with the ruthlessness of a pirate king, while accompanied by his esoteric Hamadrya. His Tyrantâ€™s Claw is a bionic relic whose crackling talons tear through armour before the in-built incineration unit unleashes gouts of sulphurous fire.','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> Tyrantâ€™s Claw; exalted weapon.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Huron-Blackheart'),(926,'Cypher','CSM',12,'Cypher is a mysterious agent of discord and insurrection, always one step ahead of capture, and strife blooms in his wake as violently as the detonations from his masterwork pistols. He is a lord of the hunted Fallen, though his true role as traitor or loyalist is as cryptic as the sword he carries but never wields.','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> Cypherâ€™s bolt pistol; Cypherâ€™s plasma pistol.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Cypher'),(928,'Fabius Bile','CSM',12,'A genius of arcane genetics, Fabius Bile enhances even the augmented biologies of his Heretic Astartes followers. With surgical precision, he wields the pain-inducing Rod of Torment in one hand, while with his other he fires toxic darts from the Xyclos Needler, as the arachnid arms of his Chirurgeon seal his own injuries.','Characters','<b>Fabius Bile is equipped with:</b> Xyclos Needler; Chirurgeon; Rod of Torment. <br><br><b>The Surgeon Acolyte is equipped with:</b> Surgeon Acolyteâ€™s tools.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Fabius-Bile'),(929,'Chaos Lord','CSM',12,'Chaos Lords have spent countless spans of mortal lives leading their traitorous warriors, demanding nothing but utter ruthlessness from those they command. Each heretic aspires to this chilling mastery, knowing there is no prize beyond their Lordâ€™s grasp and no enemy they cannot slay with pre-eminent skill.','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> plasma pistol; daemon hammer.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Chaos-Lord'),(930,'Chaos Lord In Terminator Armour','CSM',12,'Chaos Lordsâ€™ underlings expect them to fight from the front, and few kinds of armour enable them to do so as effectively as archaic Terminator plate. Formidably resilient, such a suit protects the Lord against all but the most devastating firepower and enables him to deploy by teleportation right into the heart of the foe.','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> combi-bolter; exalted weapon.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Chaos-Lord-In-Terminator-Armour'),(931,'Chaos Lord On Bike','CSM',355,'','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> bolt pistol; combi-bolter; Astartes chainsword; close combat weapon.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Chaos-Lord-On-Bike'),(932,'Chaos Lord On Juggernaut','CSM',355,'','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> bolt pistol; Astartes chainsword; bladed horn; close combat weapon.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Chaos-Lord-On-Juggernaut'),(933,'Chaos Lord On Disc Of Tzeentch','CSM',355,'','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> bolt pistol; Astartes chainsword; close combat weapon.','','false','','','','','https://wahapedia.ru/wh40k10ed/factions/chaos-space-marines/Chaos-Lord-On-Disc-Of-Tzeentch'),(934,'Chaos Lord On Palanquin Of Nurgle','CSM',355,'','Characters','<b>This model is equipped with:</b> bolt pistol; Astartes chainsword; close combat weapon; Nurgling\'s claws and teeth.','','false'